, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 482, \"end\": 489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"score\": 0.9999999467058857, \"rank\": 4.984118860737178e-08, \"text\": \"Francis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19546\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\"}, {\"begin\": 490, \"end\": 498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Brinsley_Sheridan\", \"score\": 0.6091797153121423, \"rank\": 0.6415465637131674, \"text\": \"Sheridan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Brinsley_Sheridan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Brinsley_Sheridan\"}, {\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999994443652847, \"rank\": 4.7594293161814305e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this country\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your hopes of representing your country now lie as a shattered dream.\\\"\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your hopes\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"your country\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"a shattered dream\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Van de Velde, who was released after serving only 12 months in a Dutch prison, has since been permitted to rehabilitate his Olympic career.\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.8908171103372211, \"rank\": 0.06869644152582259, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"only 12 months\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 725}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic career\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This month, he secured his spot in the national pair for the Paris Games alongside Matthew Immers.\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 904, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his spot\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"the national pair\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 878}, {\"ngram\": \"Matthew Immers\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 903}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Upon sentencing at Aylesbury Crown Court after being extradited from his homeland, his defense lawyer, Linda Strudwick, commented on the verdict: \\\"The headlines say it all: 'A sex monster.'\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 1095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 925, \"end\": 934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aylesbury\", \"score\": 0.9999999999031388, \"rank\": 9.668707531490138e-11, \"text\": \"Aylesbury\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aylesbury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aylesbury\"}, {\"begin\": 935, \"end\": 946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crown_Court\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.004624272332852e-19, \"text\": \"Crown Court\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crown_Court\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crown_Court\"}, {\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linda_McCartney\", \"score\": 0.9990194797900805, \"rank\": 0.0008990384032555827, \"text\": \"Linda\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linda_McCartney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linda_McCartney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sentencing\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"his homeland\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"his defense lawyer\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"the verdict\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"The headlines\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"A sex monster\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's plainly a career end for him.\\\"\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a career end\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has proven otherwise, as Van de Velde, now 29, has successfully rebuilt his beach volleyball career to the extent that he and Immer are now ranked as the 11th team in the world heading to Paris next month.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1324, \"end\": 1329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999728070182, \"rank\": 2.719316348975159e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"his beach volleyball career\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"the extent\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"Immer\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"the 11th team\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde's resurgence poses a significant ethical dilemma for the International Olympic Committee.\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde's resurgence\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1368}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant ethical dilemma\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each Paris Olympian is required to sign an Athletes' Rights and Responsibilities Declaration, which includes a mandate to \\\"act as a role model.\\\"\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1451, \"end\": 1456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999728070182, \"rank\": 2.719316348975159e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1457, \"end\": 1465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999994443652847, \"rank\": 4.7594293161814305e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Athletes' Rights and Responsibilities Declaration\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"a mandate\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"a role model\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having travelled from Amsterdam to Milton Keynes to engage in sexual activity with a 12-year-old girl, a fact acknowledged in strong terms by the judge in 2016, Van de Velde had previously communicated with the victim on social media before arranging the visit, during which he took her virginity while her mother was away.\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1614, \"end\": 1623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam\", \"score\": 0.999999999359261, \"rank\": 6.323974563173875e-10, \"text\": \"Amsterdam\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam\"}, {\"begin\": 1627, \"end\": 1633, \"title\": \"http://