 \"a paedophile\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That I am not, really not.\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2698, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone is entitled to their opinion about me, but it's only fair if they also hear my side of the story.\\\"\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2808, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"their opinion\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2738}, {\"ngram\": \"my side\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2793}, {\"ngram\": \"the story\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These remarks elicited a scathing response from the National Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Children, which stated: \\\"Van de Velde's lack of remorse and self-pity is astonishing, and we can only imagine how distressed his victim must feel upon seeing his comments.\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 3083, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These remarks\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2823}, {\"ngram\": \"a scathing response\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2852}, {\"ngram\": \"the National Society\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2878}, {\"ngram\": \"the Prevention\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2897}, {\"ngram\": \"Cruelty\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2908}, {\"ngram\": \"Children\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2920}, {\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde's lack\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 2956}, {\"ngram\": \"remorse\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 2967}, {\"ngram\": \"self-pity\", \"from\": 2972, \"to\": 2981}, {\"ngram\": \"his victim\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3047}, {\"ngram\": \"his comments\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thenorthlines.com is a leading digital platform covering and disseminating the news, views and allied information on evolving public policies and responses pertaining to Indian subcontinent and its neighbourhood with a particular focus on the north India region.\", \"from\": 3085, \"to\": 3347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3255, \"en